{"tid":303742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轉場! BU見!","createTime":"2017-06-30T11:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T14:28:18.000Z","uid":31739,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db81470451d8b0f7377d6fc7a5ba28a01b1c16aa","tid":303742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e2f15d673b76fa4bb751bd09dc5f7f0bd07673","tid":303742,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978bc336e7b9b3b3412624f385c174f163f1f97f","tid":303742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"【香港民族黨集會】<br />\n<br />\n今晚香港民族黨原定夜晚八點半喺尖沙嘴鐘樓舉辦集會，宣揚香港獨立理念。言論自由、集會自由都係香港人珍而重之嘅公民權利，但港共政權為完成背後嘅政治任務，竟然肆意打壓香港民族黨嘅和平集會，以「反對通知書」嘅名義阻止佢地行使港人應有嘅權利。香港民族黨亦因遭到大量警力阻撓而需要取消集會。本會對港共向市民施以行政暴力，打壓言論自由表示強烈不滿，並予以譴責；亦就香港民族黨希望宣揚獨立自主而遭到打壓感到惋惜。有見及此，本會決定連同數間大專院校，假香港浸會大學舉行記者招待會及集會，抗議港共政權濫用警力排除異己；並誠邀香港民族黨集會原定嘉賓出席。希望各位同學可以踴躍出席。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：六月三十日<br />\n時間：夜晚八點至夜晚十一點<br />\n地點：香港浸會大學本科生舍堂賽馬會廣場<br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學學生會<br />\n二零一七年六月三十日"},{"pid":"c72ed60493d6b6c0b109df89fa2c1e6876c00754","tid":303742,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"3479fca4412d0872a44115f7b0bc51797d47d442","tid":303742,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40ca52b2d0cd5c0fb5a7beb65defb61fe71dc17","tid":303742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc01ab70c22afea7516dd575be7b1d5961a43df","tid":303742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"1789年，法王路易十六反對將三級會議改為國民議會，不允許第三等級的代表進入三級會議的會場，因此後者決定在附近的室內王家網球館開會（當時已開始下雨）。在那裡，第三等級的代表們發誓將繼續開會，不制定法國憲法決不解散。除一名代表拒絕簽字外，其餘576名代表都在誓言上簽字。這是一次革命性的行動，它向世人表明，政治權利屬於人民及其代表而非君主。<br />\n<br />\n網球廳宣誓通常被認為是法國大革命誕生的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.over-blog.com/500x314/2/20/64/66/Cours-histoire/2nde/Serment-du-jeu-de-paume.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.over-blog.com%2F500x314%2F2%2F20%2F64%2F66%2FCours-histoire%2F2nde%2FSerment-du-jeu-de-paume.jpg&h=ed95cffe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1018758e48ad78cd9ca736e26d1371d09f79346","tid":303742,"uid":52842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d4be96ef44fab07cc5e13579f2f53b2e9376a8","tid":303742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c9ca8afb06bd7a689d883780d53eb997c1a3bdd","tid":303742,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/195615_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F195615_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=92408615&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1d37b73ddc386b6d5e0d980503148a58c75279d","tid":303742,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"細聲啲"},{"pid":"ce9f08e142f00f6e3ae6a8e0206c92eb764d313f","tid":303742,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img sr